    ("DATA AVAILABILITY", "we solved scaling by making everyone download the entire history — congratulations"),
    ("INTENT-CENTRIC", "users just say what they want and some solver ruins them economically — progress"),
    ("ZERO-KNOWLEDGE", "prove you know something without revealing it... except for the part where you reveal your wallet"),
    ("RESTAKING", "your staked ETH is working 3 jobs now — congratulations on becoming your own rent-seeker"),
    ("LIQUID STAKING", "be your own bank they said... now you're leveraged 47× to the moon and also to zero"),
    ("DAO GOVERNANCE", "1 person 1 vote until the whale delegation multisig says otherwise"),
    ("DECENTRALIZED IDENTITY", "finally you control your data... said no one who's ever done a zk-proof selfie"),
    ("CROSS-CHAIN BRIDGES", "trust-minimized until the moment $300M decides to take a vacation"),
    ("BLOB SPACE", "we made calldata cheap by calling it something cuter — you're welcome"),
    ("VALIDIUMS", "rollups but we pinky-promise the data is somewhere — cypherpunk style"),
    ("PRECONFIRMATIONS", "instant finality... as long as the sequencer likes you today"),
